data.description: Updated Townhome Located In Highly Sought-After Writer Community Of SouthPark. SELLER'S OFFERING A $10,000 CONCESSION TO BUYER FOR AN INTEREST RATE BUY DOWN OR TOWARDS BUYER CLOSING COSTS AT CLOSING. This Beautiful Community Features, Pool, Tennis/Sport Courts, Club House And Lots Of Walking Trails. Close To Mineral Light Rail Station And Aspen Grove Shops And Restaurants. Many Updates Including, New Roof, New Skylights, Fresh Interior Paint, New Carpet, Upper Level And Basement Area, Includes all Appliances, New Cooking Range, Private Patio, New Patio Cement, Updated Windows,   Main Floor Laundry And Main Floor Powder Room, Enter the Living Area Directly From Garage.  One Owner, Private Cul-De-Sac Location, Enjoy The Partly Finished Basement, With Open Storage Area With Lots Of Shelves And Ruff-In For Bath, Furnace, Central Air And Gas Fireplace Have Been Serviced,  Home Located in South Suburban Parks And Recreation District. Home Has Virtual Staging.  Quick Possession!
